high_descs: Turn to your right and face the fridge
Open the fridge, get the egg then close the fridge
Turn to your right then walk forward then face the sink on your left
Put the egg in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then face the table
Put the egg on the table beside the knife
anns.task_desc: Put the washed egg on the table

high_descs: Take a tiny step forward then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the egg that's under the tomato on the right side of the first shelf then close the fridge door.
Take a step or two to your right so you're in front of the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the green table.
Put the egg on the green table to the right of the yellow handled knife and slightly below it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the refrigerator on your right.
Open the refrigerator and remove the single egg from the second shelf on the right, in front of the tomato.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the kitchen sink, to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the egg in then front, right corner of the sink, turn the water on, rinse the egg off, turn the water off, and remove the egg from the sink.
Turn around and go to the kitchen island behind you.
Place the egg on the kitchen island, between the pencil and the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg on the kitchen island.
